'''大力水手炸雞'''（{{lang-en|Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen}}）又名'''-{zh-hans:大力水手炸鸡;zh-hant:大力水手炸雞;zh-tw:佰百雞;zh-hk:佰百雞;zh-cn:佰百鸡}-'''，是[[美國|美國]]的跨國連鎖[[快餐店|快餐店]]，1972年成立於[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]，公司总部位于[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[迈阿密|迈阿密]]，主要经营食品为炸雞及相关食物。连锁餐厅之前使用'''{{lang|en|Popeyes Chicken & Biscuits}}'''<ref name=AboutPopeyes>{{cite web|url=http://popeyes.com/company/about-popeyes.php|title=About Popeyes|publisher=Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen|accessdate=2017-09-12|archive-date=2012-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004234911/http://popeyes.com/company/about-popeyes.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>和'''{{lang|en|Popeyes Famous Fried Chicken & Biscuits}}'''<ref>{{Cite journal|journal={{tsl|en|New Orleans CityBusiness||New Orleans CityBusiness}}|title=Bob & Gee Tucker: Community Service Important for Married Consulting Team|volume=11|issue=6|page=23C|date=1990-09-24|author=Engelberg, Adrian}}</ref>作为餐厅名，2008年后，餐厅更名为'''{{lang|en|Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen, Inc.}}'''<ref name=Story>{{cite web |url=http://popeyes.com/our-story/ |title=Our Story |publisher=Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen |accessdate=2017-09-12 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118194620/https://www.popeyes.com/our-story |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Dodds |first=Eric |title=Happy Birthday, Popeyes Chicken |url=http://time.com/3918606/happy-birthday-popeyes-chicken/ |website=Time |accessdate=2019-02-20 |date=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119084638/https://time.com/3918606/happy-birthday-popeyes-chicken/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。佰百鸡如今是[[餐饮品牌国际|餐饮品牌国际]]旗下的[[子公司|子公司]]，餐厅品牌国际总部位于[[多伦多|多伦多]]。佰百鸡是世界上餐厅数量第二多的“鸡肉快餐餐厅”，仅次于[[肯德基|肯德基]]。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.popeyes.com/news/news.asp?n=83 |title=Popeyes Chicken & Biscuits Offers 'A Side of Hope,' to America's Hungry Families |publisher=Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen |access-date=2011-02-16 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903150041/https://www.popeyes.com/news/news.asp%3Fn%3D83 }}</ref>其在美国超过40个州、全世界30个国家或地区有3102家連鎖店。<ref name=RBI2018Report/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.caribbeanbusinesspr.com/prnt_ed/popeyes-continues-steady-international-expansion-11813.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-11-13 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117022553/http://www.caribbeanbusinesspr.com/prnt_ed/popeyes-continues-steady-international-expansion-11813.html |archivedate=2015-11-17 }}</ref>公司持有大约30家餐厅，其余为[[加盟連鎖|加盟連鎖]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hoovers.com/popeyes/--ID__105593--/free-co-factsheet.xhtml |title=Hoovers/Dun & Bradstreet: Popeyes Chicken & Biscuits |publisher=Hoovers |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070707065313/http://www.hoovers.com/popeyes/--ID__105593--/free-co-factsheet.xhtml |archivedate=2007-07-07 |access-date=2019-11-03 }}</ref>

==歷史==
大力水手炸雞於1972年6月12日在美國南部[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的[[新奧爾良|新奧爾良]]地区開設首家門店。其創辦人是當地居民Al Copeland（1944-2008）。創立時因市場目標關係，炸雞是當地口味，然擴展速度緩慢。

1976年，開始以特許經營方式開設分店，首家分店位於同州[[巴頓魯治_(路易西安納州)|巴頓魯治]]；之后十年，已於全州共有五百家門店。

大力水手炸雞於1984年起進軍海外，首家海外門店該年設於[[加拿大|加拿大]]。目前已於全球21個國和地區設有分店：包括[[日本|日本]](僅於美軍基地)、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[中國大陆|中國大陆]]、[[香港|香港]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[泰國|泰國]]等等。

2017年，大力水手炸雞以18亿美元的价格被賣予[[餐饮品牌国际|餐饮品牌国际]]，即[[汉堡王|汉堡王]]、[[蒂姆·霍顿斯|蒂姆·霍顿斯]]的母公司。

==銷售食品==
[[File:Fried-Chicken-Set.jpg|thumb]]
佰百鸡主要经营食品为炸鸡，有原味和辣味可供选择。除此以外还提供红豆、[[薯条|薯条]]、卡津风味肉汁[[土豆泥|土豆泥]]、[[鸡杂饭|鸡杂饭]]、[[芝士通心粉|芝士通心粉]]和[[凉拌卷心菜|凉拌卷心菜]]作为辅菜。除了炸鸡外，部分餐厅还有鸡肉香肠[[什锦饭|什锦饭]]和[[牡蛎穷孩儿三明治|牡蛎三明治]]等作为主菜。餐厅大多数套餐包含主菜、[[小菜|小菜]]和[[比司吉麵包|比司吉麵包]]，但不包含饮料。2006年10月30日，餐厅宣布计划在年底推出不含[[反式脂肪|反式脂肪]]的比司吉面包和仅含1克反式脂肪的薯条。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cattlenetwork.com/Content.asp?ContentID=80211 |title=Dow Jones newsire (Oct. 31, 2006): "AFC's Popeyes Chicken Plans Low Trans-Fat French Fries", by Richard Gibson |access-date=2019-11-04 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927015744/http://www.cattlenetwork.com/Content.asp?ContentID=80211 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2011年11月18日，餐厅宣布将在即将到来的[[感恩节|感恩节]]推出油炸[[三鸟烤|三鸟烤]]三明治，使用火鸡、鸭和鸡肉制作的肉饼。2013年7月29日，餐厅推出新菜油炸华夫鸡条，在部分地区受到欢迎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/24/popeyes-chicken-waffles-tenders_n_3645022.html|title=Popeyes Debuts Chicken Waffle Tenders, World Wonders Why No One Else Thought Of That Already|work=[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2013-09-06|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109021410/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/24/popeyes-chicken-waffles-tenders_n_3645022.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年佰百鸡推出限时新菜“香甜酥脆”炸鸡，用高油曲奇饼-{}-乾包裹炸鸡。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.aol.com/article/lifestyle/2017/06/19/popeyes-is-now-frying-its-chicken-in-mashed-up-cookies-heres/22489530/|title=Popeyes is now frying chicken in cookie batter – here's the flavor verdict|publisher=AOL|access-date=2017-06-22|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028173635/https://www.aol.com/article/lifestyle/2017/06/19/popeyes-is-now-frying-its-chicken-in-mashed-up-cookies-heres/22489530/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===鸡肉三明治===
2019年8月，为与[[Chick-fil-A|Chick-fil-A]]竞争，佰百鸡开始销售鸡肉三明治。部分餐厅于2019年早期为增设烤面包机等机器，对餐厅厨房重新规划。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-rise-and-fall-story-2019-8|title=Social-media battles, massive crowds, and overworked employees: Inside the rise and fall of Popeyes' chicken sandwich|last=Taylor|first=Kate|website=Business Insider|access-date=2019-09-23|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301203912/https://www.businessinsider.com/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-rise-and-fall-story-2019-8|dead-url=no}}</ref>鸡肉三明治推出后一炮走红，在社交媒体上风靡一时，并被媒体广泛报道。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thetakeout.com/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-coverage-23-million-free-press-1837582061|title=All our Popeyes' chicken sandwich coverage gave them $23 million in free press|last=Suzanne-Mayer|first=Dominick|website=The Takeout|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-26|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108000754/https://thetakeout.com/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-coverage-23-million-free-press-1837582061|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后佰百鸡的很多餐厅经常排队，导致三明治售罄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/popeyes-new-fried-chicken-sandwich-has-created-a-frenzy-in-its-stores-new-data-165231715.html|title=Popeyes' new fried chicken sandwich has created a frenzy in its stores: new data|website=finance.yahoo.com|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-26|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026022446/https://finance.yahoo.com/news/popeyes-new-fried-chicken-sandwich-has-created-a-frenzy-in-its-stores-new-data-165231715.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>原先储备的食材足够全美所有餐厅销售到9月底，然而在三明治推出后的两周以内，大量餐厅出现断货情况。<ref name="#1"/>8月27日，三明治推出约两周后，佰百鸡在推特上宣布全美所有连锁店的三明治均售罄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/27/popeyes-has-sold-out-of-its-chicken-sandwich-in-less-than-a-month.html|title=Popeyes sells out of its chicken sandwich in less than a month|last=Lucas|first=Amelia|date=2019-08-27|website=CNBC|language=en|access-date=2019-08-28|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224133914/https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/27/popeyes-has-sold-out-of-its-chicken-sandwich-in-less-than-a-month.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>一位居住在田纳西州的居民因此起诉佰百鸡公司“虚假广告”以及“商业欺诈”。 <ref>{{cite news|title=Man sues Popeyes after missing out on new chicken sandwich|url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/man-sues-popeyes-missing-chicken-sandwich/story?id=65292396|first=Kelly|last=McCarthy|date=2019-08-30|publisher=[[ABC新聞|ABC新聞]]|accessdate=2019-11-04|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226185539/https://abcnews.go.com/US/man-sues-popeyes-missing-chicken-sandwich/story?id=65292396|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年10月底，佰百鸡在其推特上宣布其鸡肉三明治于11月3日起在美国连锁店恢复供应。<ref>{{cite news |title=Popeyes braces for the return of the chicken sandwich after the original launch sparked chaos and left workers exhausted |author=Kate Taylor and Shoshy Ciment |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/popeyes-workers-ready-chicken-sandwich-return-2019-10 |website=Business Insider |date= |accessdate=2019-10-29 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202053348/https://www.businessinsider.com/popeyes-workers-ready-chicken-sandwich-return-2019-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

佰百鸡的鸡肉三明治由奶油蛋卷面包、炸鸡饼、酸黄瓜和蛋黄酱制成。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.foxnews.com/food-drink/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-a-surprise-hit-we-didnt-expect-this-type-of-reaction|title=Popeyes' chicken sandwich is surprise hit: 'We didn't expect this type of reaction'|last=Hollan|first=Michael|date=2019-08-26|website=Fox News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-26|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218191956/https://www.foxnews.com/food-drink/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-a-surprise-hit-we-didnt-expect-this-type-of-reaction|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/21/business/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-twitter.html|title=A Popeyes Chicken Sandwich and a Tactic to Set Off a Twitter Roar|last=Yaffe-Bellany|first=David|date=2019-08-21|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-08-26|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225215706/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/21/business/popeyes-chicken-sandwich-twitter.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>与其炸鸡相同，鸡肉三明治也有搭配了辣味卡津酱的版本可供选择。

